      "status": "todo",
      "title": "Improve command discoverability for getters and eval stdin semantics",
      "description": "Reduce trial-and-error for simple read-only commands and JavaScript evaluation. Dogfood found direct `title` failed instead of suggesting `get title`, and `eval --stdin` with a function-shaped snippet returned `{}` while a bare object expression worked.",
      "priority": "medium",
      "tags": [
        "dogfood",
        "docs",
        "discoverability",
        "eval"
      ],
      "scope": [
        "extensions/agent-browser/lib/results/presentation.ts",
